      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA TALK NOW (5) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 6 lengths into second (30.10) at Q Parklands in a OPEN over 520m. Rates highly and will give a great sight. EXPEDITE (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (25.52) at this track behind Mccluggage in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to be in this for a long way. BLOW BAYOU (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and four minors from nine tries. Missed the frame latest (25.63) when fourth over 457m at this track in a Restricted WIN. Can feature with the right run. TIGGY BOODIE (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
